@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ksismg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin(0.28)
    tmp = 0.97
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.68) - wp.sin(v0 + 0.22)) * v0)
    tmp = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.33 * v0 + 0.86)) * 0.62)
    v1 = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.31 - v0 + 0.52)) / v1)
    v2 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.22 + v2 + 0.89)) + wp.sin((v1 + 0.38 - v1 + 0.89)))
    tmp = (0.83 * tmp)
    v2 = (v0 * (wp.abs(v0 + 0.96) * (v2 + 0.76 + v2 + 0.19)))
    data[tid] = v0
